trans-unit.source: Indicates the window style to use for the invoked program when calling the <xref uid="langword_csharp_Shell" name="Shell" href=""></xref> function.
trans-unit.target: 指示要在调用时，可用于所调用的程序的窗口样式<xref uid="langword_csharp_Shell" name="Shell" href=""></xref>函数。

trans-unit.source: When you issue `Shell` commands, you can use the following enumeration members in your code in place of the actual values.
trans-unit.target: 当发出`Shell`可以代替实际值在代码中使用下列枚举成员的命令。

trans-unit.source: The `Style` argument takes the `AppWinStyle` enumeration members.
trans-unit.target: `Style`参数采用`AppWinStyle`枚举成员。
